{"questionId":"3301523","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The following guide is used by the coach to determine the strength of the correlation between the ranks for long jump and high jump.</p>\n<table style=\"width:359px;height:158px;border-color:#000000;margin-left:150px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:167.683px;text-align:center;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mstyle mathvariant=\"bold\"><mo stretchy=\"true\">|</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>s</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"true\">|</mo></mstyle></math></td>\n<td style=\"width:173.317px;text-align:center;\"><strong>Strength</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:167.683px;text-align:center;\">\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>000</mn></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>199</mn></math>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:173.317px;\">&nbsp; Very weak</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:167.683px;text-align:center;\">\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>200</mn></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>399</mn></math>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:173.317px;\">&nbsp; Weak</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:167.683px;text-align:center;\">\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>400</mn></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>599</mn></math>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:173.317px;\">&nbsp; Moderate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:167.683px;text-align:center;\">\n<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>600</mn></math> to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>799</mn></math>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:173.317px;\">&nbsp; Strong</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:167.683px;text-align:center;\">\n<math xmlns=\"http:/